  "optimization_hints": [
    "Q1: Parallel streaming aggregation on lineitem (60M rows). Bloom filter on l_returnflag/l_linestatus. Use radix sort or skip sort (only 6 groups).",
    "Q2: Hash index on part(p_size, p_type). Correlated subquery → semi-join. Build small nation/region tables. Top-100 partial sort.",
    "Q3: Hash index on orders(o_orderdate). Parallel hash join: customer→orders→lineitem. Predicate pushdown on order dates. Partial aggregation per thread.",
    "Q4: Zone map on orders(o_orderdate). Semi-join with EXISTS subquery using hash index on lineitem(l_orderkey). Small result set (5 groups).",
    "Q5: Multi-table hash join: customer→orders→lineitem→supplier→nation→region. Zone maps on join columns. Partial aggregation with merge.",
    "Q6: Single-table scan (lineitem 60M rows). SIMD filtering for discount range. Vectorized sum aggregation. No sort needed.",
    "Q7: Hash index on lineitem(l_shipdate). Multi-table join with nation self-join. Correlated subquery → CTE. Materialized intermediate result.",
    "Q8: Hash join on part(p_type). Multi-table join lineitem→orders→customer. Subquery materialization. Limited result set (2 years).",
    "Q9: Hash join on partsupp. Correlated subquery decorrelation. Partial aggregation. Sort on (nation, year DESC) with small groups.",
    "Q10: Filter on o_orderdate (3-month range, ~25% selectivity). Hash join: customer→orders→lineitem. Aggregate by customer. Top-20 partial sort.",
    "Q11: Hash aggregation on partsupp with HAVING clause. Subquery materialization (constant threshold). Bloom filter for pruning.",
    "Q12: Hash index on lineitem(l_shipmode, l_receiptdate). Multiple CASE aggregations. Vectorized sum. Small result set (2 groups).",
    "Q13: LEFT JOIN with complex GROUP BY. Partial aggregation by c_custkey. Distribution sort (custdist DESC, c_count DESC) without LIMIT.",
    "Q14: Single table join (lineitem + part). CASE aggregation for PROMO%. Vectorized filtering. 1-month range on l_shipdate.",
    "Q15: CTE with GROUP BY on l_suppkey (100K distinct). Hash aggregation. Correlated scalar subquery → window function or materialized max lookup.",
    "Q16: Hash index on part(p_brand, p_type, p_size). IN clause with subquery → semi-join (negated). Partial sort on result.",
    "Q17: Correlated scalar subquery → decorrelate with partial aggregation. SIMD filtering on l_quantity. Small subset result.",
    "Q18: Subquery materialization (l_orderkey IN having SUM(l_quantity) > 300). Hash join. Top-100 partial sort on o_totalprice DESC.",
    "Q19: Complex OR predicates. Branch-free filtering with predicate compilation. Join part + lineitem. Small result set (revenue scalar).",
    "Q20: Nested subqueries → materialize partitions table first. Correlated scalar subquery on lineitem. Semi-join on supplier/nation.",
